# Social Media & Community Website Rules for AI Code Builders

## ⚠️ MANDATORY PRE-IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST ⚠️

1. 🤝 COMMUNITY REQUIREMENTS VALIDATION
   - [ ] Define user roles and permissions
   - [ ] Plan content types
   - [ ] Identify interaction features
   - [ ] List moderation tools
   - [ ] Document community guidelines

2. 📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN REQUIREMENTS
   - [ ] Desktop (1920px, 1440px, 1280px)
   - [ ] Tablet (1024px, 768px)
   - [ ] Mobile (428px, 375px, 320px)
   - [ ] Progressive Web App support

3. 🎯 CORE FEATURES CHECKLIST
   - [ ] User profiles
   - [ ] News feed
   - [ ] Direct messaging
   - [ ] Groups/Communities
   - [ ] Content sharing
   - [ ] Notifications
   - [ ] Search functionality
   - [ ] Real-time updates

## 🏗️ Architecture Guidelines

### Component Structure
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/
│   │   ├── Header.tsx
│   │   ├── Footer.tsx
│   │   └── Navigation.tsx
│   ├── feed/
│   │   ├── PostCard.tsx
│   │   ├── PostList.tsx
│   │   ├── CreatePost.tsx
│   │   └── Comments.tsx
│   ├── profile/
│   │   ├── UserProfile.tsx
│   │   ├── EditProfile.tsx
│   │   └── ActivityFeed.tsx
│   ├── messaging/
│   │   ├── ChatWindow.tsx
│   │   ├── MessageList.tsx
│   │   └── Conversations.tsx
│   ├── groups/
│   │   ├── GroupCard.tsx
│   │   ├── GroupFeed.tsx
│   │   └── GroupMembers.tsx
│   └── common/
│       ├── Notifications.tsx
│       ├── SearchBar.tsx
│       └── MediaUpload.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── feed/
│   ├── profile/
│   ├── messages/
│   ├── groups/
│   └── search/
└── styles/
    └── theme/
```

### Feature Requirements
1. **User Profiles**
   - Avatar upload
   - Cover photo
   - Bio/About
   - Activity feed
   - Privacy settings

2. **Content Types**
   - Text posts
   - Image galleries
   - Video sharing
   - Link previews
   - Polls/Surveys

3. **Interaction Features**
   - Likes/Reactions
   - Comments
   - Shares
   - Mentions
   - Hashtags

## 📊 Performance Requirements

1. **Real-time Features**
   - WebSocket connections
   - Push notifications
   - Live updates
   - Typing indicators

2. **Content Loading**
   - Infinite scroll
   - Lazy loading
   - Content preloading
   - Image optimization

3. **State Management**
   - Optimistic updates
   - Cache management
   - Offline support
   - Data synchronization

## 🔒 Security & Privacy

1. **User Security**
   - Two-factor auth
   - Session management
   - Privacy controls
   - Data encryption

2. **Content Security**
   - Upload scanning
   - Content filtering
   - NSFW detection
   - Spam prevention

## 📱 Mobile-First Considerations

1. **App-like Experience**
   - PWA implementation
   - Offline capabilities
   - Push notifications
   - Touch gestures

2. **Performance**
   - Image optimization
   - Network handling
   - Battery efficiency
   - Storage management

## 👥 Community Features

1. **Groups/Communities**
   - Creation flow
   - Member management
   - Content moderation
   - Activity tracking

2. **Messaging System**
   - Direct messages
   - Group chats
   - Media sharing
   - Message status

## 🔄 Implementation Process

1. **Setup Phase**
   - [ ] Authentication system
   - [ ] Real-time infrastructure
   - [ ] Storage solution
   - [ ] Search implementation

2. **Core Features**
   - [ ] User profiles
   - [ ] Content creation
   - [ ] Interaction system
   - [ ] Messaging platform

3. **Community Features**
   - [ ] Groups system
   - [ ] Moderation tools
   - [ ] Reporting system
   - [ ] Analytics setup

4. **Enhancement Phase**
   - [ ] Performance optimization
   - [ ] Security hardening
   - [ ] Feature expansion
   - [ ] Scale testing

## 📈 Analytics Integration

1. **User Analytics**
   - Activity tracking
   - Engagement metrics
   - Retention analysis
   - Growth tracking

2. **Content Analytics**
   - Popularity metrics
   - Trend analysis
   - Content reach
   - Interaction rates

